<!DOCTYPE topic SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<topic title="Creating tabs from pages">
	<section title="Introduction" file="introducing_tabs" />
	
	<hint>Personal favorites cannot be created as tabs.</hint>
	<section title="How to create a tab from a page">
		<steps>
			<item><cref topic="signing_in_and_out_of_mingle">Sign in</cref> to Mingle and open the project with the pages you want to convert to tabs (if you're not already working in the project).
				You don't need to sign in as a project administrator.</item>
			<item><cref topic="creating_and_formatting_pages">Create the pages</cref> you want to turn into tabs (if you haven't done so already).</item>
			<item><cref topic="finding_a_page">Open the page</cref> you want to create a tab with.</item>
			<item>
				<screenshot alttext="Wiki page - make tab link" src="resources/images/wiki_page_make_tab.png" />
				<p>Click on the <link>Make tab</link> link in the page header.</p>
			</item>
			<item>
				<p>Mingle will create and highlight a new tab named the same as the page.</p>
				<screenshot alttext="Wiki page - remove tab link" src="resources/images/wiki_page_remove_tab.png" />
				<p>To remove the tab, click on the <link>Remove tab</link> link in the page header.</p>
			</item>
		</steps>
	</section>
	<section title="Also see...">
		<bullets>
			<item><cref topic="managing_favorites_and_tabs">Managing team favorites and tabs</cref></item>
			<item><cref topic="creating_tabs_from_favorites">Creating tabs from team favorites</cref></item>
			<item><cref topic="working_with_pages">Working with pages</cref></item>
		</bullets>
	</section>
</topic>


